GL_{n}(\mathbb{R}) = \{ A \in M_{n}(\mathbb{R}) \ | \ \text{det}(A) \neq 0 \}
SL_{n}(\mathbb{R}) = \{ A \in M_{n}(\mathbb{R}) \ | \ \text{det}(A) = 1 \}
GL_{n}(\mathbb{R})/SL_{n}(\mathbb{R}) \cong \mathbb{R}^{\ast}
\mathbb{R}^{\ast} \simeq \{ \pm 1 \} \times \mathbb{R}
\mathbb{R}^{\ast}
\mathbb{R}
\pm 1
H
\text{GL}_{n}(\mathbb{R}) \to (\mathbb{R}_{+},\times)
A \mapsto (\text{det}\:(A))^{2}
(\mathbb{R},+) \cong (\mathbb{R}_{+},\times)
\text{GL}_{n}(\mathbb{R}) \to (\mathbb{R}_{+},\times)
A \mapsto |\text{det}\:(A)|
(\mathbb{R},+) \cong (\mathbb{R}_{+},\times)
